            "publicNotes": "<p>Warden devils exist to capture and imprison mortals, whether as jailers in Hell or hunters summoned by diabolists. Vinculattis exercise little discretion and show less interest in a prisoner's sentence or condition. Warden devils take cruel satisfaction in heaping psychological distress on their charges, enumerating the pleasures a prisoner is now denied.</p>",
